                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7752" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1938</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2112 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“馅饼”还是“陷阱”：宁德时代的“锂矿返利”计划</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Pie&quot; or &quot;Trap&quot;: The&quot;lithium mine rebate&quot;program of CATL</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许长勇，刘杰，刘红玉，佘泽驰，左嘉霖</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宁德时代新能源科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">5 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">产业链整合；纵向整合；纵向约束；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Industrial chain integration; Vertical integration; Vertical constraints</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宁德时代，位于福建省宁德市，是一家以研发、生产和销售新能源汽车动力电池、储能系统为主，年市值过万亿，市场份额全球第一的新能源企业。宁德时代凭借强大的话语权和资金能力，向新能源动力电池产业链上下游进行纵向整合。案例描述了在锂价上涨和“退补”政策的影响下，宁德时代作为产业链的中游企业，豪掷64亿元“抢夺锂矿”和向车企推出“锂矿返利”计划，站在产业链整合的战略高度对其上下游企业进行纵向整合，以此达到优化上下游企业间的协作关系，促进企业在产业链上持续竞争力提升的目的。但是由于锂价变化趋势不定，“锂矿返利”计划的推行仍面临着极大的不确定性。本案例可用于引导学生理解和掌握纵向整合的概念和内涵，从而对纵向整合战略有更深入的理解。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">CATL, located in Ningde City, Fujian Province, is a new energy enterprise mainly engaged in R&amp;D, production and sales of new energy vehicle power batteries and energy storage systems, with an annual market value of more than one trillion yuan and the world&#39;s largest market share. With strong voice and financial capabilities, CATL has vertically integrated the upstream and downstream of the new energy power battery industry chain. The case describes that under the influence of the rising lithium price and the &quot;subsidy&quot; policy, CATL, as a midstream enterprise in the industrial chain, threw 6.4 billion yuan to &quot;grab lithium mines&quot; and launched the &quot;lithium mine rebate&quot; plan, vertically integrated its upstream and downstream enterprises from the strategic height of industrial chain integration, so as to optimize the cooperation relationship between upstream and downstream enterprises and promote the continuous competitiveness of enterprises in the industrial chain. However, due to the uncertain trend of lithium prices, the implementation of the &quot;lithium mine rebate&quot; plan is still facing great uncertainty. This case study can be used to guide students to understand and master the concept and connotation of vertical integration, so as to have a deeper understanding of vertical integration strategy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纵向整合；纵向约束；纵向并购</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-11</td>
                            </tr>
